<p>Regional media</p>
<ul>
<li>Role in education local persons about credentials of politician = more aware =&gt; less criminalisation of politics&nbsp;</li>
<li>It can<em><strong> pre election audit of funds</strong></em> of political party.&nbsp;</li></ul>
<p>Often national media, over shadows regional media.</p>
